src:
Winning numbers drawn in 'MassCash' game
03 Nov 2019, 03:23 by The Associated Press
BRAINTREE, Mass. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday evening's drawing of the Massachusetts Lottery's "MassCash" game were:
03-13-20-27-30
(three, thirteen, twenty, twenty-seven, thirty)
